ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectOrder Amending the Import Control List and Repealing the European Union Surtax Order
PrecisOrder Amending the IMPORT CONTROL LIST AND REPEALING THE EUROPEAN UNION SURTAX ORDER, in order to remove the surtax that Canada imposes on imports of beef, pork and gherkins from the European Union, in accordance with the Memorandum of Understanding signed between Canada and the European Commission on March 17, 2011.
